OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FThe captain of Morocco's World Cup
OL,8,Fteam will stand trial for rape, a
OL,9,FFrench appeals court has said.
OL,11,FAchraf Hakimi, 27, who plays for Paris
OL,12,FSaint-Germain, was accused of raping a
OL,13,F24-year-old woman at his home in the
OL,14,FFrench capital in 2023.
OL,16,FA public prosecutor's office began a
OL,17,Fpreliminary investigation and
OL,18,Frecommended in February this year that
OL,19,FHakimi should face trial, which he
OL,20,Fappealed against.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
