OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781880485
OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FOn Friday, the Versailles appeals
OL,13,Fcourt confirmed the footballer would
OL,14,Fbe formally charged with rape as there
OL,15,Fis sufficient evidence to send him to
OL,16,Ftrial.
OL,18,FThe decision comes just hours before
OL,19,FMorocco faces Scotland in their second
OL,20,Fmatch of the 2026 World Cup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781880485
OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,FHakimi, considered to be one of the
OL,8,Fbest right-backs in the world, has
OL,9,Fdenied any wrongdoing.
OL,11,FRachel-Flore Pardo, the lawyer
OL,12,Frepresenting the alleged victim, said
OL,13,Fthat after more than three years of
OL,14,Flegal proceedings, the court's
OL,15,Fdecision "brings my client a sense of
OL,16,Frelief and hope".
OL,18,F"Relief that she has been heard by the
OL,19,Fjustice system and will have her case
OL,20,Fheard at trial," Pardo said.
OL,26,@|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781880485
OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"Hope that this trial will help other
OL,8,Fwomen and further weaken the fortress
OL,9,Fof denial and impunity surrounding
OL,10,Fsexual violence, including within the
OL,11,Fworld of men's football."
OL,13,FPosting on social media on Friday, he
OL,14,Fwrote: "The justice system looked me
OL,15,Fin the eye and said, 'If you weren't
OL,16,Ffamous, there would never have been a
OL,17,Fcase.'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781880485
OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"I chose to remain silent for years. I
OL,8,Fbelieved that maintaining my dignity,
OL,9,Fbeing patient, and trusting in the
OL,10,Fjustice system would allow the right
OL,11,Fdecisions to be made.
OL,13,F"Today, a story that isn't mine is
OL,14,Fbeing told at the expense of my
OL,15,Ffamily, my life, and above all, the
OL,16,Ftruth. I sometimes feel like I've
OL,17,Fbecome an easy target.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
