PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781880485
OL,3,CMorocco captain Hakimi must stand
OL,4,Ctrial on rape charge, French officials
OL,5,Csay
OL,7,F"I've been waiting for this trial
OL,8,Fsince day one. And now I'm eagerly
OL,9,Fawaiting it. Finally, I'll be able to
OL,10,Fspeak."
OL,12,FITV News has contacted Fifa for
OL,13,Fcomment about Hakimi's appearance in
OL,14,FFriday's World Cup game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
